      "name": "Synthesis of prior pedicle screw FEA validation studies",
      "description": "A comprehensive synthesis of multiple prior peer-reviewed validation studies examining FEA predictions of spinal implant mechanical behavior under ASTM F1717 loading conditions. This synthesis aggregates findings from Rohlmann et al. (2001), Goel et al. (2006), and Natarajan et al. (2008), establishing the modeling assumptions, material property ranges, and mesh density thresholds that underpin the current ensemble approach. The convergence of these independent studies provides strong contextual support for the credibility of the current FEA framework."
    }
